.DT
set_value
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_value

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_value -  This method sets the value of the object.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_value(int number)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^number%^RESET%^ - the new value of the object
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/basic/misc.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the value of the object.  The actual value in
coins and so forth is worked out by the money handler based on the
value.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_value(), adjust_value(), query_money_array()

.EP

